-- Kouchner Sent Sarkozy His Resignation Letter in August, RTL Radio Reports
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-09-27T07:17:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/kouchner-sent-sarkozy-his-resignation-letter-in-august-rtl-radio-reports.html
French Foreign Minister Bernard
Kouchner expects to leave his post, having sent a resignation
letter to President Nicolas Sarkozy in August, RTL radio station
said.  In a report on its website, RTL cited off-air comments made
by Kouchner on a visit to Haiti.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  